<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11773>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 16. Vadumasonium vardyorum sp. n., ♀, holotype, but 9 and 16 of holotype of Vadumasonium volatum (Mason), ♀. 1 wings 2 mesosoma dorsal 3 apex of antenna 4 first-third metasomal tergites dorsal 5 head frontal 6 head dorsal 7 hind leg lateral 8 detail of fore wing postero-basally 9 first tergite dorsal 10 antenna 11 base of antenna 12 inner hind claw 13 habitus lateral 14 ovipositor 15 apex of ovipositor lateral 16 clypeus frontal. 1, 7, 10, 13, 14: scale-line (= 1.0 x); 2, 4 - 7: 1.7 x; 3: 2.5 x; 8, 9, 16: 2.0 x; 11, 12, 15: 5.0 x." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11773" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

